terraform taint resource address => to mark a resource for replacement
terraform untain <resourceaddress> => to mark a resoruce to not be replicate_source_db
TF_LOG env var => to set the verbosity of terraform logs "export TF_LOG=DEBUG"
TF_LOG_PATH env var => to store terraform logs in a file "export TF_LOG_PATH=/tmp/logs"
docs : https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/internals/debugging